            "title": "滬指開市跌5點 深成指升3點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段微跌，上證綜指以3374點開市，跌5點或0.15%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報10995點，升3點或0.04%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌5點或0.15%，開報3972點；創業板指數開市報2277點，跌4點或0.19%。</p>\n</div>",
