            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報23500點，升39點，較上日現貨收市價23477點高水22點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5868點，升9點，高水9點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報8673點，升8點，高水6點。</p>\n</div>",
